          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A 400 mug/cm**2 thick, self-supported natural",
                "silicon target was used from O1593001 for Li-6 beam",
                "210 mu-g/cm2 thick, self-supported natural silicon",
                " target-from D0355001 for Li-7 beam"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Reaction products were identified by",
                "a delta-E-E telescope with a 50 mum delta-E or 25 mum",
                "delta-E,depending on the lithium energy, and a 2000 mum",
                "E-detectors."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The probabilities(P(R)(E(n)), obtained as",
                "the ratio between the number of reaction events(E",
                "events) divided by the total number of incident",
                "particles(delta-E+E events) are connected with the",
                "energy integrated reaction cross section sigma(R) via",
                "the following formulae-",
                "Sigma(R)=-mln(1-P(R)(E(n))/N(A)R(max), where m is the",
                "target mass, number P(R) is the reaction probability,",
                "N(A) is the Avogadro's number and R(max) is the range",
                "of Li ions."
              ]
            }
          ],
